Test scores for two beginning statistics classes

Data for Exercises 1.70 and 1.87

Format

A data frame with 31 observations on the following 2 variables.

Class1
a numeric vector
Class2
a numeric vector

References

Kitchens, L. J. (2003) Basic Statistics and Data Analysis. Duxbury

Examples


str(Statisti)
#> 'data.frame':	31 obs. of  2 variables:
#>  $ Class1: int  81 73 86 90 75 80 75 81 85 87 ...
#>  $ Class2: int  87 77 66 75 78 82 82 71 79 73 ...
#> 
attach(Statisti)
boxplot(Class1,Class2,names=c("Class 1","Class 2"),col=c("red","blue"),
main="Problem 1.87")
detach(Statisti)
